    "shotList": "Scenes of purported Unidentified Flying Objects (UFOs), including purported Flying Saucers. Reel 1: 24' 1) LS of three unidentified flying objects followed by cluster of UFOs. 64' 2) MS of bird flying, then sudden appearance of white saucer-shaped objects, which might also be birds in distance. 87' 3) LS five UFOs. 99' 4) MS two UFOs flying by apparent oil derrick. 138' 5) CU man in cowboy outfit smoking cigarette with UFO in background across sky. 165' Total footage in reel. Reel 2:  10' 1) MS of repeating glow in upper right frame. 180' 2) CU small saucer-like objects moving on what appears to be television screen or motion picture screen with finger pointing out different objects. 280' Total footage in reel.",
